name: Artist: Rella | Rella artist's painting style
description:
Rella Style LoRA

中文 | English

仿Rella的作画风格的LoRA模型。

权重建议值：1 (or 0.6~1.5)

基于模型：Anything-5RE

训练信息：共计378张原画（含裁剪图），迭代1134步，多分辨率迭代训练。

其他的一些建议：可以考虑使用中景、全身视角，只是可以考虑。画面尽量华丽点。

LoRA model with a painting style imitating Rella.

Recommended weight value: 1 (or ranging from 0.6 to 1.4).

Based on the model: Anything-5RE.

Training information: A total of 378 original paintings (including cropped images) were used for training, with 1,134 iterations using multi-resolution iteration training.

Other suggestions: It is recommended to consider using mid-range or full-body perspectives, but this is just a suggestion. Make it as gorgeous as possible.
